dc_title_s: Roads Fond du Lac County, WI 2018
dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2018. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Roads_2017.gdb. [The roads layer depicts road centerlines and address ranges for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation and online dataset download, please visit http://www.fdlco.wi.gov/departments/departments-f-m/land-information/data-download.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
